---
import { profileConfig } from '../config'
import { url, getPostUrlBySlug } from '../utils/url-utils'
import { getSortedPosts } from '../utils/content-utils'

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear()
const days = new Date().getTime() - new Date('2024/04/20').getTime()
const numberOfDays = (days / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)).toFixed()

const posts = await getSortedPosts()
const latest = posts[0]
const latestDate = latest
  ? `${latest.data.published.getFullYear()}-${String(latest.data.published.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0')}-${String(latest.data.published.getDate()).padStart(2, '0')}`
  : ''
---

<div class="transition border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/15 my-10 border-dashed mx-32"></div>
<div class="transition border-dashed border-[oklch(85%_0.01_var(--hue))] dark:border-white/15 rounded-2xl mb-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6">
    <div class="transition text-50 text-sm text-center">
        本站的所有文章、界面（有另外声明的除外）均在
        <a class="transition link text-[var(--primary)] font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.zh-hans">
            署名-非商业性使用-相同方式共享 4.0 国际 (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)
        </a>
        许可协议下提供。<br />
        如果您需要转载上述内容，请附带来源，并且不可将其使用于商业用途。<br />
        © 2024-{currentYear} {profileConfig.name}. 本站已运行 {numberOfDays} 天。<br />
        {latest && (
          <>
            最近更新：
            <a class="transition link text-[var(--primary)] font-medium" href={getPostUrlBySlug(latest.slug)}>
              {latestDate} · {latest.data.title}
            </a>
            <br />
          </>
        )}
        <a class="transition link text-[var(--primary)] font-medium" href={url('/rss.xml')}>RSS 订阅</a>
        {' · '}
        Powered by <a class="transition link text-[var(--primary)] font-medium" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/saicaca/fuwari">Fuwari</a>
    </div>
</div>
